Package org.enhydra.shark.api.client.wfmc.wapi

Provides a Java binding of WfMC Interface 2/3 (WAPI v.1.0).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WAPI
    Enables client applications to connect to and interact with a workflow engine.
